{"tid":1243488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局指電腦系統從來沒與警方系統聯繫","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:14:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"071b43166adc6e514aeeb2308bfec59807f02278","tid":1243488,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"醫管局表示，「重大事件調查及災難支援系統」 屬於警務處掌管的電腦軟件系統，有關資料透過加密形式以電郵傳送，醫管局電腦系統與「重大事件調查及災難支援系統」，從來沒有任何聯繫。於「沙士」疫情之後，醫管局再沒有以類似形式傳送資料，醫管局希望有關病人私隱的評論，均建基於事實，避免打擊醫患關係，影響病人信心。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，「重大事件調查及災難支援系統」用作調查重大事件及支援災難的資料分析及身份比對之用，「沙士」疫情期間，透過相關系統的運算能力接觸追查，以控制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n立法會醫學界議員陳沛然在立法會表示，根據立法會文件，「重大事件調查及災難支援系統」相連醫管局及警方的電腦系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463881-20190619.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463881-20190619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu6Fdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=1abe8a10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463881-20190619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a26fee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463881-20190619.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46594cb64928aacfa796f3ca3d2bebff45a8c0e0","tid":1243488,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7536521e15c8e07c97f0e8d23a567a9195da2e","tid":1243488,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:11:27.000